@startuml ambient_pulse_phase_render_path_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Ambient Pulse Phase Render Path\n(BCM ambient output -> IVI pulse phase -> cabin animation)

participant "BCM\nambient mode/color/pattern owner" as BCM #E8F7E8
participant "IVI\nambient animation renderer" as IVI #E8F0FE
participant "UiRender / Infotainment\nruntime mirrors" as Render #FFF4CC
participant "Ambient output panels" as Panels #F4F7FB

== Ambient Surface Inputs ==

activate BCM
BCM -> IVI : Body::ambientMode\nBody::ambientColor\nBody::ambientPattern
note right of BCM
Ambient base state is already
resolved by BCM before IVI renders it.
end note
deactivate BCM

== Pulse Phase Derivation ==

IVI -> IVI : if alertType == 4\nor emergency alert active\nthen gAmbientPulsePhase = (phase + 1) & 3
IVI -> IVI : else gAmbientPulsePhase = 0
IVI -> Render : UiRender::ambientPulsePhase
note right of IVI
Pulse phase is a renderer-side
animation state, not a BCM-owned
ambient contract.
end note

== Cabin Frame Rendering ==

IVI -> IVI : deriveCabinAmbientAnimFrame(\nrenderMode, renderColor,\nrenderPattern, roadZoneColorCode,\nroadFlowDirection, alertLevel,\nemergencyType, ambientPulsePhase)
IVI -> Render : UiRender::renderMode /\nrenderColor / renderPattern
IVI -> Render : Infotainment::cabinAmbientAnimFrame
note right of IVI
Representative outputs
- UiRender::ambientPulsePhase
- UiRender::renderMode / Color / Pattern
- Infotainment::cabinAmbientAnimFrame
end note

== Visible Animation Outcome ==

activate Panels
Render -> Panels : cabin ambient animation frame\nand render mirrors
deactivate Panels

note over BCM, Panels
Representative runtime chain
1. BCM publishes ambient base state
2. IVI derives pulse phase from warning/emergency context
3. IVI converts ambient state + pulse phase into cabin animation frame
4. Panels consume render mirrors and cabinAmbientAnimFrame
end note

@enduml
